## Phase8 — Expanded Powerups & UX *(shipped)*

**Goal:** More variety and strategy on court without breaking the labeled-orb + court-half collector model from Phase7.

### Design rules (carry forward)

- Each powerup = **colored circle + white first letter** (`Powerup.tsx`, `POWERUP_LABELS`, `POWERUP_COLORS`)
- Collector default = court-half owner on ball hit or tap (**AI** left/top, **You** right/bottom)
- Duration default = **5 s** unless noted; avoid infinite stacking — refresh timer or cap stacks
- Portrait: consider subtle **AI / You** tint on orb so half-court ownership is obvious

### Tier 1 — Paddle modifiers *(easy; same pattern as G/S)*

Extend `PowerupType` + `applyPowerup()` in `GameScreen.tsx` (paddle shared values).

| Label | Color (suggested) | Type | Effect on target paddle | Notes |
|-------|-------------------|------|-------------------------|-------|
| **G** | Blue `#007AFF` | Grow | Height × 1.5 | ✅ Shipped (Phase7) |
| **S** | Red `#FF3B30` | Shrink | Height × 0.6 | ✅ Shipped (Phase7) |
| **F** | Cyan `#32ADE6` | Fast | AI speed × 1.4 or player drag responsiveness | ✅ `aiSpeedMultiplierSV` / `playerInputMultiplierSV` |
| **T** | Green `#34C759` | Thick | Paddle short-edge × 1.4 | ✅ Per-paddle `leftPaddleWidthSV` / `rightPaddleWidthSV` |
| **N** | Orange `#FF9500` | Narrow | Paddle short-edge × 0.7 | ✅ Same width SVs |
| **K** | Purple `#AF52DE` | Sticky | Ball attaches ~300ms on hit, then releases with aim | ✅ `leftSticky` / `rightSticky` + attach countdown |

### Tier 2 — Ball modifiers *(medium; `ballPhysics.ts`)*

| Label | Color (suggested) | Type | Effect | Notes |
|-------|-------------------|------|--------|-------|
| **B** | Yellow `#FFCC00` | Boost | Ball speed × 1.25 for 3s or next 3 paddle hits | ✅ `ballSpeedMultiplierSV` (3s duration) |
| **C** | Teal `#5AC8FA` | Curve | Slight spin / magnus on wall & stone bounces | ✅ Tangential nudge per frame via `curveActiveSV` |
| **M** | White `#FFFFFF` | Multi | Brief 2-ball rally | ✅ Secondary ball slot + 5s timeout |
| **R** | Pink `#FF2D55` | Reverse | Flip `vx`/`vy` once on collect | ✅ One-shot flip on primary ball |

### Tier 3 — Court / tactical *(medium; stones + spawn logic)*

| Label | Color (suggested) | Type | Effect | Notes |
|-------|-------------------|------|--------|-------|
| **O** | Brown `#A2845E` | Obstacle | Spawn 1 temporary stone (~8s) | ✅ `placeTemporaryStone()` + timeout remove |
| **X** | Gray `#8E8E93` | Clear | Remove nearest stone to orb | ✅ `removeNearestStone()` |
| **Z** | Indigo `#5856D6` | Zone | Invert or disable center `zoneMult` slow for 5s | ✅ `zoneMultDisabledSV` |

### Tier 4 — Mind-game *(high fun)*

| Label | Color (suggested) | Type | Effect | Notes |
|-------|-------------------|------|--------|-------|
| **A** | Blue ring | Ally | Buff **collector** | ✅ Same as grow on collector paddle |
| **E** | Red ring | Enemy | Debuff **opponent** (invert collector) | ✅ Shrink on opponent paddle |
| **?** | Gold `#FFD60A` | Mystery | Random effect from Tier 1–2 pool | ✅ `rollMysteryType()` on collect |

### UX & balance *(Phase8 polish)*

- [x] **HUD active effects** — small icons beside AI / You scores (e.g. `G↑` `S↓` with countdown)
- [x] **Orb lifetime pulse** — shrink or flash in last 2s of `POWERUP_LIFETIME`
- [x] **Buff vs debuff rings** — blue outline = helps collector; red = hurts opponent; gold = mystery
- [x] **Difficulty spawn bias** — Easy: more Grow near losing player; Hard: more Enemy / Mystery
- [x] **Stacking rules** — same type refreshes duration; conflicting effects (Grow + Shrink) cancel or pick stronger
- [x] **Stone hit feedback** — soft haptic (`ImpactFeedbackStyle.Soft`) + quieter tap sound (38% volume) on stone bounce

### Ball & multi-ball stability *(post-Phase8 hardening)*

- [x] **Primary ball render decoupled** — `Ball` always drawn from `primaryBX`/`primaryBY` during gameplay (not gated on `ballsRef.length`)
- [x] **Immutable ball pool** — `setBallEntries()` replaces array; never `.push`/`.splice` on JS after worklet touches `ballsRef`
- [x] **Multi-ball crash fix** — **M** uses `setBallEntries([primary, secondary])`; Reanimated "cannot add a new property" avoided
- [x] **Cold restart serve** — `courtReady` (`courtBounds.width/height > 0`) before Start; `pendingServeSideRef` + `useEffect` backup when Start tapped early
- [x] **App resume recovery** — `AppState` `'active'` → `recoverActiveMatchBall()` if pool empty or attach stale

### Suggested implementation order

1. **E — Enemy** (invert target; biggest strategic depth, low code)
2. **B — Boost** (one speed multiplier SV; feels great with stones)
3. **M — Multi** (use existing ball slot pool)
4. **HUD active effects** (players understand paddle size changes)
5. Remaining Tier 1 paddle mods → Tier 3 court → Tier 4 Mystery

