## Resolved Questions

1. Both orientations rotatable on menus → `"default"` in `app.json`
2. Portrait gameplay → top/bottom paddles; landscape → left/right
3. Rotation during play → **lock to starting orientation** (mid-game relayout abandoned after QA)
4. HUD active effects → **shipped** — `HudActiveEffect` chips in `ScoreBoard` (`G↑`, `B»`, etc.)
5. Tablet-specific orientation lock → deferred (play lock applies on tablets too)
6. Powerup letters → **16 types**; collector = court-half owner; **E** debuffs opponent; **?** rolls mystery
7. More powerup types → ✅ Phase8 shipped (see tiers above)
8. Opening serve → **player first** (`OPENING_SERVE_SIDE = 0`); tap-to-serve on player attach only
9. Paddle off-court after grow → fixed via `clampPaddlesToCourt` + per-frame `updateAiPaddle`
10. Court color → **Classic** (default green) or **Random** (6-color palette); intro toggle; roll on start/play again
11. Missing ball on app restart → fixed via measured-court-only `beginMatch`, `courtReady` Start gate, primary ball shared-value render, `setBallEntries` immutable pool
12. Multi-ball crash → fixed via `setBallEntries` replace (no `.push` on worklet-frozen array)

